KANSAS CITY BRIDGE COMPANY, a Corporation, Appellant, v. ALABAMA STATE BRIDGE CORPORATION, a Corporation, Appellee. No. 6524. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. July 20, 1932.

Before BRYAN, SIBLEY, And HUTCHESON, Circuit Judges. •

PER CURIAM.

The petition for rehearing in the above numbered and entitled cause is denied
